## Overview

Welcome to game zone - a mini-games project featuring two exciting 1v1 games. This project includes Tic Tac Toe, a classic game for friendly duels on a single screen or in an online room using WebSockets, and TypeTest, a game inspired by MonkeyType with a custom caret and a results page.
